<template>
    <Header />

    <Footer />
</template>

<script>
import Header from '@/components/Header.vue'
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.vue'
import { mapGetters, mapActions } from 'vuex'


export default {
    name: 'Home',
    components: {
        Header,
        Footer
    },
    computed: {
        ...mapGetters(['isLoggedIn'])
    },
    methods: {
        ...mapActions(['logout'])
    }
}
</script>
